Reflex.SayString:
Scanning rocks reveals their type.
Lava rocks are less likely to contain Phylosilicates and score fewer points. Use the laser to Beam them (press "B" button) and save your drills for higher value rocks.
Sedimentary rocks are more likely to contain Phylosilicates and score more points. Use your drill to Inspect them (press "X" button) to maximise your score.
